{"type":"message","id":"16de5f75","parentId":"876cedda","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:26:43.013Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 16th, 2026 - 6:26 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-16 10:26 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776335202956}}
{"type":"message","id":"46a6de08","parentId":"16de5f75","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:26:47.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the session startup sequence as instructed in SOUL.md and AGENTS.md.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md (already loaded in context)\n2. Read USER.md (already loaded in context)\n3. Read memory files for today and yesterday\n4. Read session context from context.json\n5. Read the most recent session summary\n\nLet me start by checking the memory files and session summaries.","thinkingSignature":"870bbd4ed7744fe92c178c2999c8c6b5c1c4ff7e92e99a2092094a50f9480f45"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bvu4655ucv0i_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ 2>/dev/null | sort | tail -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bvu4655ucv0i_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json 2>/dev/null | head -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":169,"cacheRead":21036,"cacheWrite":145,"totalTokens":21404,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0002028,"cacheRead":0.0012621599999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000054375,"total":0.0015355349999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776335203068,"responseId":"062fec61af89e0d6e345277cc33ff398"}}
