tion.md\nollama-search.md\npdf.md\nperplexity-search.md\nplugin.md\nreactions.md\nsearxng-search.md\nskills-config.md\nskills.md\nslash-commands.md\nsubagents.md\ntavily.md\nthinking.md\ntts.md\nvideo-generation.md\nweb-fetch.md\nweb.md\nagent-tools.md\narchitecture.md\nbuilding-extensions.md\nbuilding-plugins.md\nbundles.md\ncommunity.md\nmanifest.md\nmemory-wiki.md\nsdk-channel-plugins.md\nsdk-entrypoints.md\nsdk-migration.md\nsdk-overview.md\nsdk-provider-plugins.md\nsdk-runtime.md\nsdk-setup.md\nsdk-testing.md\nvoice-call.md\nwebhooks.md\nzalouser.md","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776335526387}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b52ab6c","parentId":"d58398d1","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:32:10.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me also check the cron/queue/hooks docs to round out the picture.","thinkingSignature":"3d95734bd584514ce10e9f98763bd6175b1db397d89cbf8b3c769b1b08ae1b47"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4v7la91pd7wy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/queue.md","limit":50}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4v7la91pd7wy_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/automation/hooks.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15523,"output":141,"cacheRead":21036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36700,"cost":{"input":0.004656899999999999,"output":0.0001692,"cacheRead":0.0012621599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00608826}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776335526471,"responseId":"062feda503c9a88767455e1f62d02007"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8555783","parentId":"3b52ab6c","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:32:11.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4v7la91pd7wy_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Command queue design that serializes inbound auto-reply runs\"\nread_when:\n  - Changing auto-reply execution or concurrency\ntitle: \"Command Queue\"\n---\n\n# Command Queue (2026-01-16)\n\nWe serialize inbound auto-reply runs (all channels) through a tiny in-process queue to prevent multiple agent runs from colliding, while still allowing safe parallelism across sessions.\n\n## Why\n\n- Auto-reply runs can be expensive (LLM calls) and can collide when multiple inbound messages arrive close together.\n- Serializing avoids competing for shared resources (session files, logs, CLI stdin) and reduces the chance of upstream rate limits.\n\n## How it works\n\n- A lane-aware FIFO queue drains each lane with a configurable concurrency cap (default 1 for unconfigured lanes; main defaults to 4, subagent to 8).\n- `runEmbeddedPiAgent` enqueues by **session key** (lane `session:<key>`) to guarantee only one active run per session.\n- Each session run is then queued into a **global lane** (`main` by default) so overall parallelism is capped by `agents.defaults.maxConcurrent`.\n- When verbose logging is enabled, queued runs emit a short notice if they waited more than ~2s before starting.\n- Typing indicators still fire immediately on enqueue (when supported by the channel) so user experience is unchanged while we wait our turn.\n\n## Queue modes (per channel)\n\nInbound messages can steer the current run, wait for a followup turn, or do both:\n\n- `steer`: inject immediately into the current run (cancels pending tool calls after the next tool boundary). If not streaming, falls back to followup.\n- `followup`: enqueue for the next agent turn after the current run ends.\n- `collect`: coalesce all queued messages into a **single** followup turn (default). If messages target different channels/threads, they drain individually to preserve routing.\n- `steer-backlog` (aka `steer+backlog`): steer now **and** preserve the message for a followup turn.\n- `interrupt` (legacy): abort the active run for that session, then run the newest message.\n- `queue` (legacy alias): same as `steer`.\n\nSteer-backlog means you can get a followup response after the steered run, so\nstreaming surfaces can look like duplicates. Prefer `collect`/`steer` if you want\none response per inbound message.\nSend `/queue collect` as a standalone command (per-session) or set `messages.queue.byChannel.discord: \"collect\"`.\n\nDefaults (when unset in config):\n\n- All surfaces → `collect`\n\nConfigure globally or per channel via `messages.queue`:\n\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    queue: {\n\n[40 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776335531894}}
{"type":"message","id":"02ece0a1","parentId":"b8555783","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:32:12.055Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4v7la91pd7wy_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Hooks: event-driven automation for commands and lifecycle events\"\nread_when:\n  - You want event-driven automation for /new, /reset, /stop, and agent lifecycle events\n  - You want to build, install, or debug hooks\ntitle: \"Hooks\"\n---\n\n# Hooks\n\nHooks are small scripts that run when something happens inside the Gateway. They are automatically discovered from directories and can be inspected with `openclaw hooks`.\n\nThere are two kinds of hooks in OpenClaw:\n\n- **Internal hooks** (this page): run inside the Gateway when agent events fire, like `/new`, `/reset`, `/stop`, or lifecycle events.\n- **Webhooks**: external HTTP endpoints that let other systems trigger work in OpenClaw. See [Webhooks](/automation/cron-jobs#webhooks).\n\nHooks can also be bundled inside plugins. `openclaw hooks list` shows both standalone hooks and plugin-managed hooks.\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\n# List available hooks\nopenclaw hooks list\n\n# Enable a hook\nopenclaw hooks enable session-memory\n\n# Check hook status\nopenclaw hooks check\n\n# Get detailed information\nopenclaw hooks info session-memory\n```\n\n## Event types\n\n| Event                    | When it fires                                    |\n| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------ |\n| `command:new`            | `/new` command issued                            |\n| `command:reset`          | `/reset` command issued                          |\n| `command:stop`           | `/stop` command issued                           |\n| `command`                | Any command event (general listener)             |\n| `session:compact:before` | Before compaction summarizes history             |\n| `session:compact:after`  | After compaction completes                       |\n| `session:patch`          | When session properties are modified             |\n| `agent:bootstrap`        | Before workspace bootstrap files are injected    |\n| `gateway:startup`        | After channels start and hooks are loaded        |\n| `message:received`       | Inbound message from any channel                 |\n| `message:transcribed`    | After audio transcription completes              |\n\n[254 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776335531972}}
{"type":"message","id":"a96906f5","parentId":"02ece0a1","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:32:17.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very comprehensive picture. Let me also quickly check the cron jobs and streaming sections.","thinkingSignature":"6c401c60c5c71627ef5f4ea35af675dec9244d757d0b18cbf320639019e7a3c0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e9eks4ss8ape_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/automation/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16711,"output":72,"cacheRead":21036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37819,"cost":{"input":0.0050133,"output":0.0000864,"cacheRead":0.0012621599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00636186}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776335532056,"responseId":"062fedab63ac7d615cd8b1a7cdf0a861"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a75034c5","parentId":"a96906f5","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:32:18.616Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e9eks4ss8ape_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"auth-monitoring.md\nclawflow.md\ncron-jobs.md\ncron-vs-heartbeat.md\ngmail-pubsub.md\nhooks.md\nindex.md\npoll.md\nstanding-orders.md\ntaskflow.md\ntasks.md\ntroubleshooting.md\nwebhook.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":813,"aggregated":"auth-monitoring.md\nclawflow.md\ncron-jobs.md\ncron-vs-heartbeat.md\ngmail-pubsub.md\nhooks.md\nindex.md\npoll.md\nstanding-orders.md\ntaskflow.md\ntasks.md\ntroubleshooting.md\nwebhook.md","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776335538535}}
{"type":"message","id":"41a86ca6","parentId":"a75034c5","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:33:26.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive view. Let me compose the full detailed overview.","thinkingSignature":"ecb52a1f8532c404e0d0ce387fbd5e85c2478afa780c67339b9b5f707ed214bb"},{"type":"text","text":"好，这是 OpenClaw 的完整功能框架，**一个都不落**：\n\n---\n\n# OpenClaw 完整功能框架\n\n## 一、核心定位\n\n**OpenClaw = 多渠道 Gateway + 本地 AI 推理引擎**\n\n- 部署在自己的机器/服务器，数据完全自主可控\n- 一个进程同时对接所有聊天渠道\n- 支持多 Agent 并存（每个 Agent 有独立 Workspace + 认证 + 会话）\n\n---\n\n## 二、架构图\n\n```\n聊天平台（Discord/Telegram/WhatsApp/飞书/Signal/Slack/飞书等）\n                    ↓\n           Gateway（3100端口，单一进程）\n                    │\n        ┌───────────┼────────────┐\n        ↓           ↓            ↓\n   渠道路由     Session管      Hook/自动化\n   Channel     理 + Hook       + Cron\n   Router       System\n        │\n        ├→ Agent（主推理引擎）\n        │     ├→ Bootstrap Files（SOUL/AGENTS/IDENTITY/USER/MEMORY）\n        │     ├→ v8 Router（3102）→ 微服务栈\n        │     │     ├→ 3103 Scorer（评分引擎）\n        │     │     └→ 3105 Classifier（场景分类器）\n        │     └→ Tool Orchestrator（工具编排）\n        │\n        └→ Web Control UI（18789端口）\n              ├→ Chat（对话）\n              ├→ Config（配置）\n              └→ Sessions（会话管理）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、渠道层（Channel）\n\n**内置渠道（Built-in）：**\nDiscord、Google Chat、iMessage（legacy）、IRC、Signal、Slack、Telegram、WebChat、WhatsApp\n\n**捆绑插件渠道（Bundled）：**\nBlueBubbles（iMessage）、飞书、LINE、Matrix、Mattermost、Microsoft Teams、Nextcloud Talk、Nostr、QQ Bot、Synology Chat、Tlon、Twitch、Zalo\n\n**可选独立渠道插件：**\n语音通话（Voice Call）、微信（WeChat，第三方）\n\n**功能：**\n- 群聊支持（mention 激活规则）\n- DM 白名单 + 设备配对\n- 跨平台同时在线\n\n---\n\n## 四、Agent 系统\n\n### 4.1 运行时\n- 嵌入式 Agent 运行时（Tool streaming）\n- 多 Agent 路由（按 Workspace 或发送者隔离会话）\n- 流式输出 + Chunk 分片\n\n### 4.2 模型支持（35+ 提供商）\n- Anthropic / OpenAI / Google\n- DeepSeek / MiniMax / 硅基流动 / 月之暗面 / 智谱\n- 自托管：Ollama、vLLM、SGLang\n- 任何 OpenAI-compatible 或 Anthropic-compatible 端点\n- OAuth 认证（如 OpenAI Codex）\n- 支持 TTS / 语音合成\n\n### 4.3 模型配置策略\n| 配置项 | 作用 |\n|--------|------|\n| `primary` | 主模型 |\n| `fallbacks` | 降级顺序 |\n| `imageModel` | 图片分析专用 |\n| `pdfModel` | PDF 解析专用 |\n| `imageGenerationModel` | 图片生成 |\n| `videoGenerationModel` | 视频生成 |\n| `musicGenerationModel` | 音乐生成 |\n\n### 4.4 多 Agent 隔离\n每个 Agent 拥有独立的：\n- **Workspace**（文件 + SOUL.md + AGENTS.md）\n- **State dir**（认证配置 + 模型注册）\n- **Session store**（聊天历史）\n- **Auth profiles**（不共享，需手动复制）\n\n---\n\n## 五、三层记忆系统\n\n| 层级 | 文件 | 作用 | 加载时机 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| 瞬时层 | `ephemeral/*.jsonl` | 每轮决策原始日志 | 实时 |\n| 会话层 | `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary-*.md` | Session 摘要 | /new 时注入 |\n| 长期层 | `MEMORY.md` | 精选记忆 | 主会话 DM 自动加载 |\n\n**记忆工具：**\n- `memory_search` — 语义搜索（支持向量 + 关键词混合）\n- `memory_get` — 精确读取文件/行\n\n**记忆后端（可切换）：**\n- **Builtin（默认）**：SQLite，向量相似度 + 关键词混合搜索\n- **QMD**：本地优先，带重排和查询扩展，可索引 Workspace 外目录\n- **Honcho**：AI 原生跨会话记忆，用户建模，多 Agent 感知\n\n**记忆 Wiki（可选插件）：**\n- 编译持久记忆为结构化 Wiki（金丝雀页面 / 矛盾追踪 / 新鲜度跟踪 / 仪表盘）\n\n**自动记忆刷新：**\n压缩（Compaction）前自动将重要上下文写入记忆文件，无需手动干预。\n\n**Dreaming（实验性）：**\n- 后台记忆整理pass，将短期信号评分后升入长期记忆\n- 需手动开启，有Cron调度\n- 输出到 `DREAMS.md` 供人类审查\n\n---\n\n## 六、任务路由（v8 评分/分类系统）\n\n```\n用户消息\n    │\n    ├→ POST 3103 Scorer → { score, factors, recommendedStrategy }\n    │    评分维度：逻辑/风险/时长/资源/不确定性/依赖链\n    │\n    └→ POST 3105 Classifier → { scene, confidence, meta }\n         场景分类：clarify / task / troubleshoot / chat / info\n\n评分档位：\n0-20  → DIRECT（单步）\n20-40 → STEP_ARCHIVE（简单多步）\n40-60 → SUBAGENT（复杂，spawn子agent）\n60-80 → PARALLEL（多任务并行）\n80-100 → MEGA（超复杂，编排）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、工具系统（Tools）\n\n| 类别 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| **文件** | read / write / edit |\n| **执行** | exec / process |\n| **Git** | via exec |\n| **搜索** | web_search / web_fetch |\n| **浏览器** | agent-browser CLI |\n| **子 Agent** | sessions_spawn / sessions_send |\n| **定时** | cron（精确调度）/ heartbeat（心跳轮询） |\n| **多媒体** | image_generate / video_generate / music_generate |\n| **图像分析** | image |\n| **语音** | openai-whisper（本地STT）|\n| **会话** | sessions_list / sessions_history / sessions_send |\n| **记忆** | memory_search / memory_get |\n| **网页** | browser自动化（Edge CDP / Playwright）|\n\n**浏览器自动化：**\n- Windows Edge CDP 方案（绕过 headless Chromium 国内风控）\n- 支持签到/填表/截图/信息抓取\n\n**Skills 市场（ClawHub）：**\n- 按需加载技能（飞书/GitHub/天气/视频提取/OCR等）\n- 支持自己编写发布到 clawhub.ai\n\n---\n\n## 八、自动化系统\n\n### 8.1 Cron 调度器\n- `at`：一次性精确时间\n- `every`：间隔（毫秒）\n- `cron`：标准 cron 表达式 + 时区支持\n- 支持 session 绑定（main / isolated / current / session:xxx）\n- 支持 webhook POST 回调\n\n### 8.2 Hooks（事件驱动）\n| 事件 | 触发时机 |\n|------|----------|\n| `command:new` | /new |\n| `command:reset` | /reset |\n| `command:stop` | /stop |\n| `session:compact:before` | 压缩前 |\n| `session:compact:after` | 压缩后 |\n| `agent:bootstrap` | Bootstrap文件注入前 |\n| `gateway:startup` | Gateway启动后 |\n| `message:received` | 收到消息 |\n| `message:transcribed` | 语音转录完成 |\n\n### 8.3 消息队列模式（per channel）\n- `collect`：合并为单次followup（默认）\n- `steer`：注入当前运行\n- `followup`：当前运行结束后排队\n- `steer+backlog`：注入+保留followup\n- `interrupt`：中止当前运行，执行新消息\n\n---\n\n## 九、会话管理\n\n- **DM 会话**：同一 sender 折叠为共享 `main` session\n- **群聊**：每个群独立 session\n- **Subagent**：独立 isolated session\n- **Session Pruning**：自动裁剪超长会话\n- **Compaction**：自动摘要 + 上下文压缩\n- **Streaming**：长回复分块流式输出\n- **Typing Indicator**：队列等待时即时显示对方正在输入\n\n---\n\n## 十、媒体支持\n\n| 类型 | 方向 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 图片 | 收/发 | 生成 + 分析 |\n| 音频 | 收/发 | TTS + 语音转录 |\n| 视频 | 收/发 | 生成 |\n| 文档 | 收/发 | PDF解析 |\n\n---\n\n## 十一、移动节点（Nodes）\n\n| 平台 | 能力 |\n|------|------|\n| **iOS** | 配对 / 语音 / 聊天 / Canvas / 相机 / 录屏 / 位置 |\n| **Android** | 配对 / 语音 / 聊天 / Canvas / 相机 / 设备命令 |\n| **macOS** | 菜单栏伴侣 App |\n\n配对流程：设备身份 → Gateway配对审批 → 设备Token → 后续自动认证\n\n---\n\n## 十二、Web UI（Control UI）\n\n- 默认地址：`http://127.0.0.1:18789/`\n- 功能：聊天 / 配置 / 会话管理 / 节点管理\n- 远程访问：Tailscale / SSH隧道\n\n---\n\n## 十三、安全机制\n\n- 设备身份 + 配对审批\n- WebSocket 握手 + Token 认证\n- Tailscale Serve 模式（头部认证）\n- `gateway.auth.allowTailscale: true` 时跳过共享密钥\n- 非可信入口建议 `gateway.auth.mode: \"none\"` 关闭\n- 消息幂等性 Key（防重复执行）\n- 沙箱执行（可选 Workspace 隔离）\n\n---\n\n## 十四、配置方式\n\n**配置文件：** `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n**两种模式：**\n1. **开箱即用**（0配置）：使用内置 Pi binary，per-sender session\n2. **自定义配置**：指定渠道白名单、mention 规则、模型提供商\n\n---\n\n## 十五、CLI 命令\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start/stop/restart/status   # Gateway 管理\nopenclaw onboard                            # 向导式初始化\nopenclaw dashboard                          # 打开 Control UI\nopenclaw hooks list/enable/check/info       # Hook 管理\nopenclaw memory status/search/index         # 记忆管理\nopenclaw models list/set/scan               # 模型管理\nopenclaw tasks                              # 后台任务\nopenclaw status                             # 当前状态\nopenclaw help                               # 完整帮助\n```\n\n---\n\n## 十六、当前运行状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 端口 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Gateway | ✅ 在线 | 3100 |\n| v8 Scorer | ✅ 在线 | 3103 |\n| v8 Classifier v2 | ✅ 在线 | 3105 |\n| WebChat Control UI | ✅ | 18789 |\n| Cron 调度器 | ✅ 正常 | — |\n\n---\n\n还有什么想深入了解的具体模块？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16852,"output":2433,"cacheRead":21036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40321,"cost":{"input":0.0050555999999999995,"output":0.0029196,"cacheRead":0.0012621599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00923736}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776335538617,"responseId":"062fedb19977364707b9dc99b34babb9"}}
