{"type":"message","id":"ad848ffa","parentId":"c1517988","timestamp":"2026-04-16T11:03:12.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there's any conflict between the new features from 2026.4.14 and the existing framework documentation I wrote. Let me think about this.\n\nLooking at the new features:\n1. Active Memory - adds a new plugin and configuration\n2. Context Engine - adds a new plugin slot and architecture\n3. Codex Provider - new provider, no conflict\n4. LM Studio Provider - new provider, no conflict\n5. Usage Tracking - MiniMax coding-plan tracking - I already covered usage tracking but maybe need to update\n6. Retry Policy - per-channel retry - I covered this\n\nThe main things that might conflict with or need updates to my existing framework:\n\n\n- My framework mentioned \"三层记忆系统\" - Active Memory is a new layer on top, doesn't conflict\n- \"插件系统\" - Context Engine is a new plugin slot type, consistent\n- \"模型系统\" - Codex and LM Studio are new providers, consistent\n- \"Usage Tracking\" - I covered this in section 34, consistent\n- \"Retry Policy\" - I covered this in section 35, consistent\n\nThe only thing I'm noticing is that my \"当前运行状态\" section still shows the old version number, which needs updating to reflect the new 2026.4.14 release.","thinkingSignature":"65d206130c6999dd14e3bb7e547cb8c86e89ba6e798e71d16b5e80a8807d53dd"},{"type":"text","text":"没有实质冲突。新功能都是在现有架构上加层或开槽位，不动既有设计：\n\n| 新功能 | 与现有框架关系 |\n|--------|--------------|\n| Active Memory | 叠加在\"三层记忆\"之上，新增插件层 |\n| Context Engine | 新增 `plugins.slots.contextEngine` 槽位，不影响 legacy |\n| Codex / LM Studio Provider | 扩展\"35+ 提供商\"列表 |\n| Usage Tracking | 已在 §34 覆盖，MiniMax 部分需微调 |\n| Retry Policy | 已在 §35 覆盖 |\n| 安全修复 | 全部是内部修复，不改接口 |\n\n唯一需要更新的是 §34 的 Usage Tracking — MiniMax 部分我写得不够精准（coding-plan 细节），以及 §19 模型列表可以加上 LM Studio / Codex 这两个新 provider。\n\n要我现在改这两处吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":439,"cacheRead":102671,"cacheWrite":13878,"totalTokens":117042,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005268,"cacheRead":0.00616026,"cacheWrite":0.0052042500000000005,"total":0.01190751}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776337372185,"responseId":"062ff4dbce7e57a1880fcde649f76328"}}
