[Thu 2026-04-16 19:01 GMT+8] 有什么新功能\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): CHANGELOG.md\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 11:## 2026.4.14\n87:## 2026.4.12\n168:## 2026.4.11\n203:## 2026.4.10\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): # Changelog\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n## Unreleased\n\n### Changes\n\n### Fixes\n\n## 2026.4.14\n\n### Changes\n\n- OpenAI Codex/models: add forward-compat support for `gpt-5.4-pro`, including Codex pricing/limits and list/status visibility before the upstream catalog catches up. (#66453) Thanks @jepson-liu.\n- Telegram/forum topics: surface human topic names in agent context, prompt metadata, and plugin hook metadata by learning names from Telegram forum service messages. (#65973) Thanks @ptahdunbar.\n\n### Fixes\n\n- Agents/Ollama: forward the configured embedded-run timeout into the global undici s...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ## 2026.4.10\n\n### Changes\n\n- Models/Codex: add the bundled Codex provider and plugin-owned app-server harness so `codex/gpt-*` models use Codex-managed auth, native threads, model discovery, and compaction while `openai/gpt-*` stays on the normal OpenAI provider path. (#64298)\n- Memory/Active Memory: add a new optional Active Memory plugin that gives OpenClaw a dedicated memory sub-agent right before the main reply, so ongoing chats can automatically pull in relevant preferences, context, and past details without making users remember to manually say \"remember this\" or \"search memory\" first. I...\n- Assistant: 从 2026.4.9 升到 2026.4.14，跨越 5 个版本，变更非常多。核心新功能和重大改进：\n\n---\n\n## 🔥 重大新功能\n\n### Active Memory（2026.4.10+）\n阻塞式记忆子 agent，在主回复生成前主动检索注入相关记忆。解决了传统记忆\"被动等待\"的问题。\n\n### Context Engine 插件化（2026.4.10+）\n可插入的上下文引擎架构，支持替换 legacy 引擎，实现更高级的上下文压缩策略。内置 `lossless-claw` 等第三方引擎。\n\n### Codex 捆绑 Provider（2026.4.10+）\n`codex/gpt-*` 模型现在走 Codex 自有认证、线程、模型发现和压缩，不再依赖 OpenAI provider。\n\n### LM Studio Provider（2026.4.12+）\n新增官方 LM Studio 集成，支持本地/自托管 OpenAI-compatible 模型，包含模型发现、流式 preload 和 memory-search embeddings。\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 功能增强\n\n| 功能 | 版本 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Telegram Forum Topics** | 2026.4.14 | 话题名称注入上下文，支持持久化 |...\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-16 19:02 GMT+8] 跟现有框架有什么冲突吗\n- Assistant: 没有实质冲突。新功能都是在现有架构上加层或开槽位，不动既有设计：\n\n| 新功能 | 与现有框架关系 |\n|--------|--------------|\n| Active Memory | 叠加在\"三层记忆\"之上，新增插件层 |\n| Context Engine | 新增 `plugins.slots.contextEngine` 槽位，不影响 legacy |\n| Codex / LM Studio Provider | 扩展\"35+ 提供商\"列表 |\n| Usage Tracking | 已在 §34 覆盖，MiniMax 部分需微调 |\n| Retry Policy | 已在 §35 覆盖 |\n| 安全修复 | 全部是内部修复，不改接口 |\n\n唯一需要更新的是 §34 的 Usage Tracking — MiniMax 部分我写得不够精准（coding-plan 细节），以及 §19 模型列表可以加上 LM Studio / Codex 这两个新 provider。\n\n要我现在改这两处吗？\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<read-files>\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/CHANGELOG.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/automation/cron-jobs.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/automation/hooks.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/automation/taskflow.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/channels/index.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/active-memory.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-loop.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/architecture.md\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/compaction.md\n...and 34 more\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/Ope