{"type":"message","id":"9e6fe6b9","parentId":"f0995264","timestamp":"2026-04-16T11:12:32.707Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i0e6cqmb1msd_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│\n◇  Config warnings ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                         │\n│  - plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (memory slot set to  │\n│    \"memory-core\") but config is present                                 │\n│                                                                         │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (memory slot set to \"memory-core\") but config is present\nSkills (25/60 ready)\n┌───────────────┬───────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────┐\n│ Status        │ Skill                     │ Description                                           │ Source           │\n├───────────────┼───────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────┤\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-doc             │ Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when  │ openclaw-extra   │\n│               │                           │ user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links. │                  │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-drive           │ Feishu cloud storage file management. Activate when   │ openclaw-extra   │\n│               │                           │ user mentions cloud space, folders, drive.            │                  │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 feishu-perm            │ Feishu permission management for documents and files. │ openclaw-extra   │\n│               │                           │ Activate when user mentions sharing, permissions,     │                  │\n│               │                           │ collaborators.     