mprovement. Use when: (1) A        │                  │\n│               │                           │ command or operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User     │                  │\n│               │                           │ corrects Claude ('No, that's wrong...', 'Actually...  │                  │\n│               │                           │ '), (3) User requests a capability that doesn't       │                  │\n│               │                           │ exist, (4) An external API or tool fails, (5) Claude  │                  │\n│               │                           │ realizes its knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6)  │                  │\n│               │                           │ A better approach is discovered for a recurring task. │                  │\n│               │                           │ Also review learnings before major tasks.             │                  │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 v8_classifier          │ OpenClaw v8 场景分类器。调用 3105                     │ openclaw-managed │\n│               │                           │ API，将用户消息分类为9种意图场景（闲聊/任务/故障/     │                  │\n│               │                           │ 模糊等）。用于理解用户消息的底层意图，配合 v8_scorer  │                  │\n│               │                           │ 做路由决策。                                          │                  │\n│ ✓ ready       │ 📦 v8_scorer              │ OpenClaw v8 任务复杂度评分引擎。调用 3103             │ openclaw-managed │\n│               │                           │ API，评估任务复杂度并返回执行策略。用于判断用户任务应 │                  │\n│               │                           │ 走 DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA 哪种执行路径。  │                  │\n└───────────────┴───────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────┘\n\nTip: use `openclaw skills search`, `openclaw skills install`, and `openclaw skills update` for ClawHub-backed skills.","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776337952683}}
{"type":"message","id":"5074dcd7","parentId":"9e6fe6b9","timestamp":"2026-04-16T11:12:39.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the memory plugin status and a few more things.","thinkingSignature":"ba53da69dd104617e10cec2cb91d27a5a03d973f9117fb1c355987123c8eda2f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5jb0cf87x84t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\npl=d.get('plugins',{})\nprint('=== memory plugin config ===')\nprint('slot:', pl.get('slots',{}).get('memory'))\nprint()\nents=pl.get('entries',{})\nfor k,v in ents.items():\n    if 'memory' in k.lower() or 'active' in k.lower():\n        print(k+':', json.dumps(v, indent=2))\nprint()\nprint('=== active-memory ===')\nif 'active-memory' in ents:\n    print(json.dumps(ents['active-memory'], indent=2))\nelse:\n    print('not configured')\nprint()\nprint('=== contextEngine slot ===')\nprint(pl.get('slots',{}).get('contextEngine','not set (using legacy)'))\n\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5jb0cf87x84t_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/ 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35750,"output":247,"cacheRead":21798,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57795,"cost":{"input":0.010725,"output":0.0002964,"cacheRead":0.00130788,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012329280000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776337952709,"responseId":"062ff71f330d20c5008f875494a7ac52"}}
