have their own separate workspaces rather than using the shared one, which contradicts the framework's assumption of a single global workspace.\n\nNow I'm examining the model configuration to see how the primary and fallback models are actually configured in the system.","thinkingSignature":"863102a8eff5b871c22ae8206bf6c4629c748721a174f8ba7d8ee50fb384f2ca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qugw147v3lni_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\npl=d.get('plugins',{})\nents=pl.get('entries',{})\nfor k in ['active-memory','context-engine','lossless-claw']:\n    print(k+':', json.dumps(ents.get(k,'not present'), indent=2))\n\" 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qugw147v3lni_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw models list 2>&1 | grep -E \"^(Provider|minimax|deepseek|ollama|volcengine|codingplan)\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36236,"output":631,"cacheRead":21798,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58665,"cost":{"input":0.0108708,"output":0.0007572,"cacheRead":0.00130788,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01293588}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776337960376,"responseId":"062ff728e85ab3c00a4931bbf1dc2a7e"}}
