{"type":"message","id":"3a3d5cae","parentId":"5843e592","timestamp":"2026-04-16T11:17:45.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the structure clearly. The memory-core entry ends with `},\\n      \"openclaw-weixin\":`. I need to:\n\n1. Remove the entire `memory-lancedb` block (including the trailing comma after `}`)\n2. Add `active-memory` block after `memory-core` block (before `openclaw-weixin`)\n\nLet me construct the exact oldText carefully.","thinkingSignature":"60b1c9275dc93992c54c4640816020523af07beb6bc5e4a205cd0a8ff5a2dd91"},{"type":"text","text":"好，现在清楚了。用 Python 直接修改 JSON 更可靠：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x80cltyp9j3x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\npath = '/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json'\nwith open(path) as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n\nentries = d['plugins']['entries']\n\n# 1. Remove orphaned memory-lancedb\nentries.pop('memory-lancedb', None)\n\n# 2. Add active-memory after memory-core (insert before openclaw-weixin)\n# Build the new block\nactive_memory = {\n    \"enabled\": True,\n    \"config\": {\n        \"enabled\": True,\n        \"agents\": [\"main\"],\n        \"allowedChatTypes\": [\"direct\"],\n        \"queryMode\": \"recent\",\n        \"promptStyle\": \"balanced\",\n        \"timeoutMs\": 15000,\n        \"maxSummaryChars\": 220,\n        \"logging\": True\n    }\n}\n\n# Insert active-memory key after memory-core\nkeys = list(entries.keys())\nidx = keys.index('memory-core')\nentries.insert(idx + 1, 'active-memory', active memory)\n\n# Rewrite\nwith open(path, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"Done. Verifying...\")\n\n# Verify\nwith open(path) as f:\n    d2 = json.load(f)\nents = d2['plugins']['entries']\nprint(\"Keys:\", list(ents.keys()))\nprint(\"active-memory:\", json.dumps(ents.get('active-memory'), indent=2))\nprint(\"memory-lancedb present?:\", 'memory-lancedb' in ents)\nEOF"}}],"api":"ant