{"type":"message","id":"e744df5f","parentId":"28b561af","timestamp":"2026-04-16T11:32:43.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scoring and classification ARE being captured in the ephemeral files. \n\n- Classification: `scene: \"clarify\"`, confidence: 0.365\n- Scoring: score: 62, recommendedStrategy: \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\"\n\nSo the answer is: **Yes, both scoring (3103) and classification (3105) are triggered on every user message**, and the results are written to the ephemeral JSONL files.\n\nHowever, the current scene shown is \"clarify\" which means the classifier isn't getting the full context. This is a separate issue from the Active Memory question.\n\nLet me verify this is the latest data and that the scoring is happening in real time for the current session.","thinkingSignature":"7e0f3c2e4816cc6ef14c0eb5cfe6371734188159a00bdf68f7e8dd41cfe45a2d"},{"type":"text","text":"**是的，每次消息都触发。** 数据都写在 ephemeral 日志里：\n\n```\nclassification → scene: \"clarify\"  confidence: 0.365\nscoring       → score: 62  recommendedStrategy: \"SPAWN_SUBAGENT\"\n```\n\n这是刚才那条消息的评分记录：**score=62，分到 SPAWN_SUBAGENT 档位**。\n\n评分和分类的调用链路：\n\n```\n用户消息\n    ↓\nGateway（入口层）\n    ├──→ POST 3103/api/score  → { score, factors, strategy }\n    └──→ POST 3105/classify   → { scene, confidence, meta }\n    ↓\n结果写入 ephemeral/YYYY-MM-DD-XX.jsonl（实时）\n    ↓\nActive Memory sub-agent（独立运行）\n    ↓\n主 Agent 回复生成\n```\n\n两者是并行的，都属于消息入口层的路由决策，和 Active Memory 的 blocking sub-agent 是分开的两条流水线。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":62050,"output":338,"cacheRead":21798,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84186,"cost":{"input":0.018615,"output":0.0004056,"cacheRead":0.00130788,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02032848}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776339153984,"responseId":"062ffbd0225352d8654f912e879836b8"}}
