{"type":"message","id":"3f075973","parentId":"11dbd83e","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:15:40.910Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-16 20:15 GMT+8] 点击发送之后，我这边要等时间才会看到我的信息发出去了"}],"timestamp":1776341740855}}
{"type":"message","id":"7835de50","parentId":"3f075973","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:16:01.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says after clicking send, they have to wait before they see their message appear in the chat. This means the bottleneck is between the UI and the gateway - either the gateway isn't receiving the message, or it's receiving it but not confirming it back to the UI.\n\nThis could be because:\n1. The session is tied to a `main` agent that doesn't exist anymore (unknown agent id \"main\")\n2. The gateway is stuck processing something and not acknowledging new messages\n\nLet me check what agent the webchat session is actually using. The fact that `unknown agent id \"main\"` appears suggests that the webchat might be trying to use the \"main\" agent, which doesn't exist in the config.\n\n\nI'm seeing `unknown agent id \"main\"` in the logs, but the active-memory plugin references \"main\" as its target agent - yet active-memory is now deleted from the config. The webchat session is connected to the gateway at localhost:3102 and likely defaulting to the \"main\" agent, which doesn't exist in the agents list since only fast_agent and deep_agent are configured.\n\nThis is probably the core issue - the webchat is trying to use a \"main\" agent that no longer exists, so messages never get processed because there's no agent to handle them. The solution would be adding \"main\" back to the agents list, either as a new agent or by renaming one of the existing ones.","thinkingSignature":"99373360aaab27a45196b65400cf5bfe220a61de0340087092c9b94f5301a560"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了。\n\n日志里有个关键错误：\n```\nunknown agent id \"main\"\n```\n\n你的 webchat 消息路由到 `main` agent，但配置里没有 `main`——只有 `fast_agent` 和 `deep_agent`。\n\n所以消息发出去后，gateway 在尝试把消息投递给一个不存在的 agent，卡住等待超时，然后才返回错误。你看到的就是\"等很久才发出\"。\n\n**需要把 `main` agent 加回配置：**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xzsq32n6z20l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('agents.list:', json.dumps(d.get('agents',{}).get('list',[]), indent=2))\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":460,"cacheRead":104420,"cacheWrite":2065,"totalTokens":107003,"cost":{"input":0.0000174,"output":0.000552,"cacheRead":0.006265199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000774375,"total":0.007608975}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776341740964,"responseId":"063005ec8ef12b35e6cb88ad6dd7b4d1"}}
