{"type":"message","id":"9fe080bd","parentId":"fadeabc3","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:24:21.931Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture of the restart:\n\n1. `20:16:09 config change detected; evaluating reload (agents.list)` - this confirms the config change was hot-reloaded\n2. `20:16:09 config hot reload applied (agents.list)` - main agent was added back\n3. `20:16:13 SIGTERM` - graceful shutdown\n4. `20:16:17 webchat disconnected code=1012 reason=service restart` - Control UI disconnected\n5. `20:16:20 loading configuration...` - new process starting\n6. `20:16:24 [plugins] plugins.allow is empty...` - plugins loading\n\n\n7. The gateway restarted and Control UI reconnected, but the user's messages still aren't showing up in the logs. I'm wondering if the issue is that the Control UI is routing through localhost:3102 while I'm monitoring the primary gateway on 3102, but there might be a separate Control UI server running on 18789 that's handling the webchat separately.\n\nLet me check the gateway status to see what ports it's actually listening on.","thinkingSignature":"26f612d3be38a5b4ee38e72ee931ec1aeb11368db30077a3697fc3dca80c1707"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了！`20:16:09 config hot reload applied (agents.list)` 说明 main agent 已经热重载进去了。但重启后 webchat 断开了，Control UI 需要重连。\n\n日志往下看：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3e133b16d70648b2bf0157a0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-16.log | grep -E \"(20:16:4|20:17|20:18|20:19|20:20|20:21|20:22)\" | grep -v \"sessions.list\\|chat.history\\|handshake timeout\" | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    try:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        t = d.get('time','')[:19]\n        msg = str(d.get('1', d.get('0','')))[:130]\n        print(t, msg)\n    except:\n        print(line.strip()[:130])\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1611,"output":440,"cacheRead":115200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117251,"cost":{"input":0.0004833,"output":0.0005279999999999999,"cacheRead":0.006912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0079233}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776342252429,"responseId":"063007eb621852eaae1d14ed2616c6e2"}}
