{"type":"message","id":"11f6458c","parentId":"b463eec2","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:27:10.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the session transcript clearly. The session IS receiving messages and the agent IS responding. The last entries show:\n\n1. A toolResult at 12:26:49 (my exec command output)\n2. An assistant message at 12:26:57 with `stopReason: \"toolUse\"` - this means the agent called a tool (my exec command)\n\nThis means:\n- Messages ARE arriving at the agent\n- The agent IS processing them and responding\n- The session is active and healthy\n\nThe user's complaint about \"发出去信息要等时间\" (messages take time to send) seems to be about something else. Maybe it's the **Control UI** display lag - the user types a message, sends it, but the UI doesn't immediately show the message in the chat history, making it seem like it hasn't been \"sent\" yet.\n \nSo the message does reach the agent and gets processed, but there's a delay between when the user sends it and when it actually appears in their chat interface. The issue isn't with the agent's processing time - it's the UI feedback lag that's bothering them.\n\nLooking at the timestamps more carefully, there's a 8-14 second gap between when the user says they sent a message and when it shows up in the transcript. This could be the Control UI not immediately displaying the sent message, or there's a delay before the agent starts processing it. I need to figure out where exactly this delay is happening - whether it's in the UI layer or if the gateway itself is slow to receive and route the message. The user is sending messages through webchat and seeing them appear in the transcript, so they are reaching the agent. But there's clearly a delay somewhere - maybe the issue is that the user sees the message in the UI but then has to wait for the AI to process and respond. Let me check the session list output to see if there's an active agent run consuming resources, and also look at the current state of the main session to understand what's happening.","thinkingSignature":"44a15619dcc5326a7ac392af0f3e0c9ba52edeef11fadd9881e09fe3770d3a2d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSession 是活跃的，消息在 12:26:57 有 agent 回复。说明消息确实在处理。\n\n问题可能在别处。让我看 session 列表里 `agent:main:main` 当前状态：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b11cb697cbc34c21978f528f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw sessions 2>&1 | grep \"agent:main\" | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1094,"output":501,"cacheRead":122752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124347,"cost":{"input":0.0003282,"output":0.0006012,"cacheRead":0.007365119999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00829452}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776342418028,"responseId":"063008911114253d51e06223dbbc1f2d"}}
