{"type":"message","id":"2d2b5a4b","parentId":"a9272d9b","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:31:06.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The user is saying TWO things are slow:\n1. After clicking send, the message takes time to appear on screen\n2. After the message appears, the reply also comes slowly\n\nBoth are slow. The gateway and model are working, but the overall experience is slower than before the update.\n\nThe key clue: \"远没有更新前的速度快\" - before the update it was faster.\n\nThis strongly suggests something changed in the v2026.4.14 update that affected performance. Possible candidates:\n1. The `think:adaptive` mode is on for this session\n2. Something about the model routing or the way messages are processed changed\n3. Some new feature is adding overhead\n\nLet me check if there's a way to see the actual processing time for messages - specifically looking at when a message enters the gateway vs when the response starts coming back.\n\nActually, let me look at the most recent session more carefully. The session `agent:main:main` has `think:adaptive` in its tags. This is probably the main culprit.\n\nLet me check when the last user message was sent and how long the agent took to respond.\n\n\nThe thinking mode is likely the primary issue here - it's making the model do extra work that slows down the entire response cycle. I should ask the user to disable thinking mode or test with a fresh session to see if that resolves the performance degradation.","thinkingSignature":"6f275ca0d4e74f9ed82882cf2782009bfd5f3e83af159842a33e7486678c2e3e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这就清楚了——升级后整个链路变慢了，不只是某个环节。\n\n最可能的根本原因：**`think:adaptive`**。这个模式让模型边推理边输出思考过程，额外消耗时间和 tokens。\n\n当前 session 正好是 `think:adaptive` 模式，122k context 加上 thinking，开销很大。\n\n两个验证方法：\n\n**方法 A**：发个 `/think off` 看有没有用（有些版本支持）\n\n**方法 B**：你开一个新的 browser tab 访问 Control UI，建立全新 session，看看速度是否正常\n\n你觉得哪个方便？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":165,"output":395,"cacheRead":125696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126256,"cost":{"input":0.0000495,"output":0.000474,"cacheRead":0.007541759999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00806526}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776342654655,"responseId":"0630097d968faf8162fe5c0b00cb4ee8"}}
