{"type":"message","id":"9d3196ec","parentId":"13af318f","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:32:22.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to take initiative and just fix it. The issue is `think:adaptive` - I should just disable it by default in the config. Let me add `thinking: \"off\"` to the agents defaults config and restart the gateway.","thinkingSignature":"38184f6e52cbc0b1d2a10220cb2cb6461ff0c3169efc126595e0c828cce53009"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，直接动手。`think:adaptive` 是罪魁祸首，关掉它：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_095f063627694b9182084129","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\npath = '/home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json'\nwith open(path) as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n\nd['agents']['defaults']['thinking'] = \"off\"\n\nwith open(path, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"thinking set to off\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":213,"output":175,"cacheRead":125824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126212,"cost":{"input":0.0000639,"output":0.00020999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.007549439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00782334}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776342734062,"responseId":"063009cdbb0abb401d1dd5b7a910eab7"}}
