{"type":"message","id":"eeacf3a1","parentId":"4ade7145","timestamp":"2026-04-16T12:36:12.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right to call me out. I've been going in circles for the past 30 minutes without solving the core problem. Let me look at what's actually happening:\n\n1. The user says messages are slow to appear after clicking send\n2. I've been focusing on gateway logs, thinking modes, active memory etc.\n3. But actually - the user's messages ARE reaching me. I can see them. So the issue isn't that messages aren't arriving.\n4. The real issue might be something much simpler - like the `thinking: adaptive` setting in the current session that's causing slow responses\n\nBut wait - the user is saying \"点发送后，消息在界面上出现的速度\" is slow. This means the UI itself is slow to show the message after clicking send. \n\nSo the bottleneck isn't the gateway or model response time - it's the Control UI rendering the message. The user confirms both the message appearing and the reply coming back are slower than before the update. The `think:adaptive` mode in this session would explain the slow reply, but that's a session-level setting and the user doesn't want me to disable thinking globally. Maybe I should focus on why the UI rendering itself is sluggish, or whether the issue is actually just about thinking mode being enabled.\n\nActually, I need to reconsider my approach here. The user said \"你遵守soul.md了吗\" - which is a sharp redirect. Looking back at SOUL.md, I should be more direct, speak Chinese as the default, be pragmatic and straightforward without being corporate or sycophantic. I've been going in circles with all the config changes, so let me stop and think about what's actually changed in v2026.4.14 that could affect UI performance. The user is experiencing slowdown in both message sending and reply speed after updating, so something in the gateway or Control UI behavior change is the real culprit here.\n\nLet me just ask the user to refresh the Control UI page and try sending a message to see if that helps isolate the issue.","thinkingSignature":"b8488ce31a3294f5aa4fa59fd20db7f02d9382a641a29463c083dc3f4181a743"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对，我绕了太久。\n\n**先做一件事**：刷新 Control UI 页面（Ctrl+Shift+R），建立一个新的 session，测试发送速度是否正常。\n\n这个测试能直接判断是旧 session 的问题（think:adaptive + 大 context）还是全局变慢。刷新后告诉我结果。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":138,"output":469,"cacheRead":126464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127071,"cost":{"input":0.0000414,"output":0.0005628,"cacheRead":0.007587839999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00819204}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776342957552,"responseId":"06300aad5dc0db0bae6c9b65ed9d5b7d"}}
